  doi           = {10.1111/jav.01180},
  groups        = {Tentatively include and/or not enough info, Maybe Include},
  review        = {propensity to excavate decreased with time since fire? They should offer some sort of mechanism. BBWO doesn't re-use cavities, so I'll need to decide if this applies to our model. },
